  "id": "2666957034_1",
  "title": "佩戴人工心脏上考场的女孩，中考喜提692分！",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content defaultNoSetting\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   近日，中考成绩发榜，国家儿童健康与疾病临床医学研究中心、国家儿童区域医疗中心、浙江大学医学院附属儿童医院（以下简称“浙大儿院”）心衰病房也迎来了喜报：\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   截至考试当天，\n   <strong>\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n     已经佩戴人工心脏778天的女孩美美（化名），喜提692分！\n    </span>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <strong>\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FxrFYciaHL08CltxgDz9eianfic7XjK01jUOa95ibDtggicDAR3iamQ086Xxb9PaaTTiaJ7bGpnuW10KibuHVpRzFL3jJjw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4060150570042966023\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4060150570042966023\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-w=\"1080\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border-radius: 4px;\">\n  </iframe>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   2023年5月，因为扩心病进入晚期心衰阶段，美美在浙大儿院植入人工心脏。四个月后，\n   <strong>\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n     她背着人工心电池设备重返校园，与同龄人一样冲刺中考。\n    </span>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   清晨6:30起床，深夜23:00熄灯，埋头苦学成为常态。“生病耽误的时间，必须争分夺秒抢回来。”美美笑着说。\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">\n  <img alt=\"2023年，美美术后佩戴人工心的照片。图片由浙大儿院提供\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"633\" data-backw=\"400\" data-imgfileid=\"519473381\" data-ratio=\"1.5826893353941267\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"647\" height=\"633\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/ibQ2cXpBDzUN98xB12fmcUfcySyFCuo1eb1lp3tBsZQUaLtbFSpwVXHsVC7o21r0ASnqdWsCuZaiccKYDcHzicmLA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;width: 1080px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" width=\"400\"/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 16px;\">\n   2023年，美美术后佩戴人工心的照片\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   当被问及在学校是否会得到格外的关照，美美又露出招牌式笑容：“其实感觉没啥区别，有些人甚至都不知道我背这个（指人工心电池设备）。”\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   洗澡时小心防水，每天精准服药，定期复查——这些日常被她轻描淡写带过：“习惯了，不影响我刷题！”\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">\n  <img alt=\"美美在学习。图片由浙大儿院提供\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"533\" data-backw=\"400\" data-imgfileid=\"519473382\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"533\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/ibQ2cXpBDzUN98xB12fmcUfcySyFCuo1e0Dxr24PNHDX8hJZ84nkZUrVsP7k9kQHNHNB8nubHniaBWCqP9rLLr1Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;width: 1080px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" width=\"400\"/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 16px;\">\n   美美在学习\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   “她像小太阳，照亮了整个病房。”浙大儿院心衰/机械辅助循环科主任林茹说，曾经，晚期心衰患儿连活下去都很艰难；如今，美美用692分证明：人工心脏托起的不仅是生命，还有滚烫的梦想。\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"383\" data-backw=\"578\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"519473370\" data-ratio=\"0.6626936829558999\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"839\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/xrFYciaHL08CltxgDz9eianfic7XjK01jUOYOz7ASKDCHuUtF02vYA0cOYSLuer3cPqcoJtvqKVpIibN3PuHtaZ3Mg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\"/>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 16px;\">\n   美美和医生合影\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   医学技术日新月异，\n   <strong>\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n     相信未来这些心衰患儿还可能得到更多新解法、遇见新希望。\n    </span>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(214, 168, 65);font-size: 18px;\">\n    美美，了不起！\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <strong>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(214, 168, 65);font-size: 18px;\">\n    加油！祝你未来一切顺利！\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\"/>\n <section>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   来源：人民网（记者：乔业琼 视频：谢地），综合浙大儿院（文：木玉），图片由浙大儿院提供\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   本期编辑：胡程远、方梓祎\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"__bg_gif rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"170\" data-backw=\"578\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xrFYciaHL08BMq1Er5otH3veEWm0Gm4EcXDCzQM0GqPIQicibBUEVGskz2ElAmhtSqbPxvdIEWBslRSvlficibUDVeg/640?\" data-imgfileid=\"519473377\" data-ratio=\"0.29444444444444445\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xrFYciaHL08BMq1Er5otH3veEWm0Gm4EcXDCzQM0GqPIQicibBUEVGskz2ElAmhtSqbPxvdIEWBslRSvlficibUDVeg/640?wx_fmt=gif\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5525px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"auto\"/>\n  <br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"